Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他吧 一騎
